{
  "stem": "10710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One day, my kapo tells me, you are assigned to-- to take out the corpses from the ground and burn them, because when they shoot people, they used to shoot them and burn them.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then came already in 1943, they were afraid that-- they didn't want to leave any-- any signs that they would shoot people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So that's why they were burning them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I knew when I go to the work, I never come out of it because they don't want to have any witnesses left later.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I still had 500 zlotys with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't know how I hid it somewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I gave the guy 500 zloty It was a goyish kapo, not a Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was a goy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I said, see, here is 500 zloty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "See maybe you can take me out of that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I was a young boy all by myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he says, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Let's see what I can do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And in the morning, he says, OK, you don't have to go there anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But people who went there-- what a work this was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "This was a smell that you smelled-- the people came into the barracks from that work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I mean, you have to burn dead people to make ash of them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They had to do it by hand and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I thought, I'll go there, I'll be finished.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I have felt that somebody was watching me all those years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I-- you know, I forgot to mention it, can I go back to-- when I was in Rabka, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in Rabka was, if you got sick, or if you couldn't work, you-- you'd be-- you-- automatically they shot you.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They put you on the list, and then next action they take you.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
